---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Emig Supply</title>
	</head>
	<body class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 transition-colors">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
			<header class="text-center mb-12">
				<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mb-4">Emig Supply</h1>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Your source for locally-made and locally-sourced items</p>
			</header>

			<section class="mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 text-center">How It Works</h2>
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
					<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">1. Request an Item</h3>
						<p>Either something from our listed inventory or something you're looking for.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">2. Negotiate a Fair Price</h3>
						<p>We work with you to find a price that works for both sides.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">3. Schedule Delivery</h3>
						<p>Arrange a convenient time for delivery to your door.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">4. Receive Your Item</h3>
						<p>The item is conveniently brought right to your door.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 text-center">Inventory</h2>
				<p class="text-center mb-6">Our inventory mostly consists of locally-made or locally-sourced items. We specialize in a wide variety of items.</p>
				<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-4">Examples</h3>
					<ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
						<li>Used power equipment (snow blowers, pressure washers, lawn mowers, etc.)</li>
						<li>Used farm trailers</li>
						<li>Used pianos</li>
						<li>Furniture</li>
						<li>Custom 3D printed designs</li>
						<li>Custom CNC wood designs</li>
						<li>Custom 3D printed designs</li>
						<li>Custom cakes</li>
						<li>Custom cupcakes</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>

			<footer class="text-center mt-12">
				<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Built by <a href="https://kwila.cloud" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Kwila Cloud</a></p>
			</footer>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
